data.description: This stunning 3 bed, 3 bath home with a walk out basement is exactly what you have been searching for. The current owners have treated this wonderful property with so much care you will be able to just move right in. The sprawling front porch offers the perfect place to welcome in guests and family. The large living room greets you as you enter the front door, over to the left you see the built in office nook. Fresh paint covers most walls and ceilings throughout. The kitchen is combined with the dining room. New laminate flooring adorns many of the rooms. The master bath has been updated. As you head into the walk out basement you enter the family room. This room has so much space. There is a full bath downstairs. The lower level laundry room has ample storage space. Rounding out this home is an attached 2 car garage, fenced in backyard, and a private deck. Whether you are looking for your first home or your next, 106 Glenwood Drive is ready for you.
